            "product_rating_description": "<p>WBCM also offers a competition-approved leather workout belt for women if they are disappointed with the support of softer fabric belts.</p><ul><li><strong>Material:</strong> Leather</li><li><strong>Sizes:</strong> 6 (S, M, L, XL, 2XL, 3XL)</li><li><strong>Waist Measurement Range</strong>: 28”-52”</li><li><strong>Closure Type:</strong> Double-prong roller buckle</li><li><strong>Width:</strong> 4” (tapered)</li><li><strong>Thickness:</strong> 6 mm</li><li><strong>Certification:</strong> IWF</li><li><strong>Colors:</strong> Black</li><li><strong>Price:</strong> $$</li></ul>",
