            "second_button_url": "https://www.amazon.com/WARM-BODY-COLD-MIND-Weightlifting/dp/B088NM97B1?tag=wbcmb-20",
            "product_text_content_1": "<p>Genuine leather is hard to beat if you're seeking all-out support and stability. It’s a lot stronger than nylon, enhancing the belt's durability, longevity, and rigidity. As a compromise, it reduces ventilation and range of motion. However, 6mm belts reserve much of these comfort factors, as opposed to thicker 10mm or 13mm powerlifting variants.</p><p><a href=\"https://warmbody-coldmind.com/products/weightlifting-lether-belt?sca_ref=5120971.qSPHd7ePgJ\" target=\"_blank\">The belt</a> comprises two layers of black leather glued together. One of them covers the dual-prong metal buckle to prevent skin contact. It's also padded, since padding isn’t prohibited by IWF rules. </p>",
            "product_review_image": "shopify://shop_images/training-best-weightlifting-belts-women-leather-wbcm-insta-819x1024.jpg",
            "half_width_review_image": true,
            "product_review_image_caption": "<p>Photo by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CXMiK5QNswK/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==\" target=\"_blank\">@warmbody_coldmind</a></p>",
            "product_text_content_2": "<p>Furthermore, the 4” back support tapers off to the half in front. It avoids digging into ribs or hips, which is the biggest issue for people with smaller torsos. Such details make it an excellent choice for women's leather weightlifting belts.  </p><p>There aren’t many drawbacks as long as you’ve got <a href=\"https://blog.warmbody-coldmind.com/guides/what-size-lifting-belt-should-i-get/\" target=\"_blank\">the correct size</a>. There is also no color variety, so you’ll have to go with the laser-printed black, which fortunately goes with everything.</p>",
            "product_pros": "<ul><li>Multi-layered, softened leather is not uncomfortably firm</li><li>Double-prong systems are more secure than single-prong or Velcro</li><li>One of the most affordable and dependable leather belts</li></ul>",
            "product_cons": "<ul><li>The range of smaller sizes can be improved</li><li>Only one color option</li></ul>"
          }
